---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Innovate, Integrate, Inspire</h1>
      <p>Rynexx Cloud Innovations is a cutting-edge technology company that offers secure and reliable cloud solutions for businesses of all sizes.</p>
      <a href="#services" class="btn">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="services" class="section">
    <h2>Why Choose Rynexx Cloud?</h2>
    <p>Our team of seasoned experts is at the forefront of the industry, bringing extensive experience and a passion for staying ahead of technology trends. We don't just implement solutions; we architect success for your business in the digital age.</p>
    <div class="services">
      <div class="service">
        <img src="/images/cloud-migration.jpg" alt="Cloud Migration">
        <h3>Cloud Migrations Redefined</h3>
        <p>Embark on a transformative journey to the cloud with precision and efficiency. Our mastery of Azure, AWS, and Google Cloud Platform ensures seamless migrations that maximize benefits and minimize disruptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <img src="/images/sd-wan.jpg" alt="SD-WAN Implementation">
        <h3>SD-WAN Implementation</h3>
        <p>Enhanced Connectivity, Reduced Costs: Rynexx Cloud's SD-WAN solutions not only improve connectivity but also bring cost-effectiveness to your network operations, providing a modern, agile approach to WAN management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <img src="/images/firewall.jpg" alt="Firewall Implementation and Management">
        <h3>Firewall Implementation and Management</h3>
        <p>Fortified Security: Implement Palo Alto firewalls with us to ensure robust network security. Our continuous monitoring and management protocols keep your systems secure from evolving cyber threats.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>